Package: hsquared
Title: Tools for H-Squared Analyses
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Shinichi", "Nakagawa", , "itchyshin@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a development home for tools to estimate, report, and
    work with h-squared quantities in R. The package is currently an early
    scaffold, with public functions to be added as the API is designed.
